## Technical Notes

- The `Analytics` component is lightweight and non-blocking
- Tracking data is sent via `/_vercel/insights/view` endpoints
- No route-specific support is available with the plain React implementation, but all page transitions tracked through React Router will still be captured
- Works seamlessly with the existing HeroUI and Tailwind CSS setup
